{"id":"22eb2374119267056c6a50c99b90b2300ffb486d6b9bb8c42750dad60e6a072f","item_id":"f45cae19de:0","text":"OpenVDB 是一种用于体积的开源分层数据结构。它已经成为应用程序之间交换体积数据的标准。有关 OpenVDB 的更多信息，请参阅"}
{"id":"0503b41b2d20e2d29da288614e349c158fc0d1efbbc21a7bd0ed13811c9da7dd","item_id":"f45cae19de:1","text":"OpenVDB FAQ"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"f45cae19de:2","text":"。"}
{"id":"4664b7ae783263be81e62106f1ebf8800fcf61b7c8e9501bf20196842f5a49ce","item_id":"f45cae19de:3","text":"从 OpenVDB 文件渲染"}
{"id":"869ee146c2092098a22086d66c221384f03cd2a39aeafd4eedf1038a5479eadd","item_id":"f45cae19de:4","text":"如果你已经有 .vdb 文件，RenderMan 会使用"}
{"id":"85baafb7076d3c42f9aca8111436fdd40a67797b340a8ddfebc06bc5b8c0e5f8","item_id":"f45cae19de:5","text":"blobbydso:impl_openvdb"}
{"id":"1d572b3f7f9af85d23b941d7229d6022b4a54251ea2d777119d1b5db4993b460","item_id":"f45cae19de:6","text":"procedural（程序过程）读取该文件，而不是把 .vdb 文件转换为 volume（体积）。"}
{"id":"e170b35362c37850742c9c26b845996f2b164a60c41ee0acebdeba8be9700116","item_id":"f45cae19de:7","text":"只需创建一个"}
{"id":"fa9da5754ccfd409028cef393a17acae922be11469a590d1f2b99d9f45349337","item_id":"f45cae19de:8","text":"Geometry（几何体）"}
{"id":"f78977016530a5a60f857314c28b3a4cf5a48f9c8f9bf02815cf8e659d6355cd","item_id":"f45cae19de:9","text":"SOP。进入该节点内部，并设置"}
{"id":"50009ce1da4d15e1c4a04024df691eed5f0d598e2c4c67092f205366d0adf99e","item_id":"f45cae19de:10","text":"File"}
{"id":"d04a88514bdc3867de163b771fb23c2fbcb1ee78f537c920161c8122a25063d0","item_id":"f45cae19de:11","text":"SOP 的"}
{"id":"db3cca9e355f95931113a8c717d2fd7f6bab1f31b20d872b5839fd0127d6a24c","item_id":"f45cae19de:12","text":"Geometry File"}
{"id":"3dcc8cc24fa31e96ae184fa7145ebc3b1610e1f7dbb31e902c8a05dc509db310","item_id":"f45cae19de:13","text":"参数，使其指向你的 .vdb 文件。"}
{"id":"71c238d0d7db2f8038b9d52ef8125697188ffdc8c65e4b5e28d4cb0c1911af4e","item_id":"f45cae19de:14","text":"这样就可以了！"}
{"id":"2dbc97647aeda9fa9cf2d78b50ffeade033db8bf9c3eaeae9edb72d9d5b7de1a","item_id":"f45cae19de:15","text":"RenderMan for Houdini 会自动检测 bounding box（边界框）和所有 VDB 网格名称。"}
{"id":"8ece895c9b32c6436d34b0384ae9f8555c8abccd31541f722f27e45e72a85bff","item_id":"f45cae19de:16","text":"将"}
{"id":"6b2b3cbd4ad476016050e61b781d1112117b06945fb578fbffcfc4ff3f6daa69","item_id":"f45cae19de:17","text":"PxrVolume"}
{"id":"0d5fe6cd1ecd5708b43a04eba982e3a49aa98309ee19f64cc2b75dffac1213bb","item_id":"f45cae19de:18","text":"或你的 volume Bxdf（体积 Bxdf）指派给 Geometry 节点。别忘了在 PxrVolume 中正确设置 density primvar（密度 primitive variable）名称（它应匹配 .vdb 文件中的 density grid（密度网格）名称）。"}
{"id":"f74efce4e9e4cdae4fcc152158b74ca2b1122b8559d0930cd181428c0a59f0ca","item_id":"f45cae19de:19","text":"如果已导出，你可以通过节点 info（信息）按钮查看可用的 primvars（图元变量）；示例包括 density、emission、temperature、velocity..."}
{"id":"92780cca1645de1ddbe3bf7f94a85e33a03545a7396d4938e2cb3b7af9335a95","item_id":"f45cae19de:20","text":"从 Houdini 体积渲染"}
{"id":"e45459f320f7a8550f85def4c168e6827db95ced2d3e1223d207bd350256ed3c","item_id":"f45cae19de:21","text":"要渲染 Houdini volume network（体积网络）或 non-VDB file（非 VDB 文件），请将其连接到"}
{"id":"c109ad66b99d4b8adabfc4793e0ef5f92a721a1051901744b4d96d47b58c58d1","item_id":"f45cae19de:22","text":"Convert VDB"}
{"id":"77228c1192c27e8f8e741239d40f7788038ed6b431f79f64912bf28fd39102eb","item_id":"f45cae19de:23","text":"SOP。将"}
{"id":"eadb1913f1cd574a043bc0d651de7635f8e3ba28b48c99b3fcd2c653f68a8f57","item_id":"f45cae19de:24","text":"“Convert To”"}
{"id":"663ea1bfffe5038f3f0cf667f14c4257eff52d77ce7f2a218f72e9286616ea39","item_id":"f45cae19de:25","text":"改为"}
{"id":"a74588a457acd2e3ffc17957d38c4a6659d09151b46f2f7c05b3af881f94e3cc","item_id":"f45cae19de:26","text":"VDB。"}
{"id":"8cbb07b215c5a439d07de16d8cb0e831972cf243022f621f6f9af0d19e3a6b34","item_id":"f45cae19de:27","text":"渲染时，RenderMan for Houdini 会自动把 .vdb 文件写出到 Houdini 临时目录。这样，我们就能利用高效的 VDB 格式，而不会发出可能变得非常庞大的 RiVolume 数据。"}
